This application is aimed at keeping track of all events done by the Play House.
Using this application is very simple.

Selecting the Add event option will allow the user to enter in all details about that event.
Please make sure that all fields are entered. No field should be blank.
Secondly, a contact number must contain 10 digits.
An error message will display if something is not entered in correctly

Selecting the show event will display all events up to date.

Selecting the send email will allow the user to write out the email message.
Tapping the send button, will re-direct the user to an email application (gmail) of their choosing.

